1. Bavim se pisanjem pesama. (I engage in writing poems.)
2. U slobodno vreme se bavim čitanjem knjiga. (In my free time, I occupy myself with reading books.)
3. On se bavi trgovinom nekretninama. (He is engaged in real estate trading.)
4. Njihova firma se bavi proizvodnjom hrane. (Their company deals with food production.)
5. Bavila sam se sportom dok nisam povredila nogu. (I used to do sports before I injured my leg.)
6. Da li se tvoj brat bavi nekim hobijem? (Does your brother have any hobbies?)
7. Ovo je posao kojim se on bavi već godinama. (This is the job that he has been doing for years.)
8. Bavićemo se ovim pitanjem na sastanku sledeće nedelje. (We will address this issue at the meeting next week.)
9. Ne mogu da se bavim ovim problemom sada, imam druge obaveze. (I can't deal with this problem now, I have other obligations.)
10. Naučiti kako se baviti stresom je važno za dobro zdravlje. (Learning how to deal with stress is important for good health.)

Note: The word "bavim" is highlighted with a star (*) in each sentence for easy identification.